- This exactly matches `20000 / num_prompts`: `16 -> 1250`, `32 -> 625`, `64 -> 312.5`.
- Catch-up jobs now override `data.train_samples=120000`, enough for 1500 steps at `num_prompts=64` (`1500 * 64 = 96000`) with margin.

